OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Falbeit fairly breezy evening with
OL,7,Fplenty of late sunshine. Staying dry
OL,8,Fovernight with prolonged clear periods
OL,9,Fand winds gradually easing. Feeling
OL,10,Fsomewhat fresher compared to last
OL,11,Fnight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FWarm in southern parts of
OL,14,Fthe region with lengthy sunny periods.
OL,15,FSomewhat cloudier, breezier and cooler
OL,16,Ffurther north with a small chance of a
OL,17,Flight shower across the Peak District.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
