OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA fine
OL,6,Ffew days on Sunday and Monday, with
OL,7,Fplenty of warm spells of sunshine and
OL,8,Flight winds. Perhaps an increasing
OL,9,Fchance of showers developing later on
OL,10,FTuesday.
